snippet.title: One Finger Death Punch 2 gameplay
snippet.description:
If you're sensitive to flashing, there's a lightning effect at 10:29 and 20:57 that I'd recommend skipping past.

The details on the characters are optional. The eyes and flesh-colored hands just help me keep track of things for some reason.
